Concerning modernizing immunization requirements for school entry to improve vaccination rates. Session: 2019 Regular Session, Subject: Public Health

Bill Summary
------------
The bill requires the department of public health and environment to:
- Develop a standardized form and submission process to claim a medical exemption to an immunization; and
- Develop a standardized form and submission process to claim a religious or personal belief exemption to an immunization.

